Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka guru bahasa Jepang kita\Nmengundurkan diri setelah menang undian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada data yang menunjukkan kalau\N78% orang ingin pensiun dini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar nanti akhirnya akan kehabisan uang\Ndan harus cari kerja lagi, sudah satu paket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anjlok?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paket sedih macam apa itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Guru bahasa Jepang yang baru nanti,\Norangnya seperti apa, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku akan senang kalau orangnya\Nsuka baca buku."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap orangnya baik dan ramah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.69,0:00:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga orangnya waras\Ndan mengajar dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya itu aspek utama dari guru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakal jadi karakter baru anime ini, lho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, yang datang mungkin\Ntipe spesialis bahasa Jepang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengetahuan bahasa Jepangnya sangat luas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bisa bicara cuma pakai kanji, misalnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi bahasa Mandarin, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Matahari, buku, terbaik, dewa."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Tipe itu, mungkin, bisa jadi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinannya 37% punya jambul samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, people dari Japan school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am datang dari Amerika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil saja aku Bu Naddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata tipe penghancur logika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}100 Pacar yang Sungguh Sangat Amat\NBenar-benar Mencintaimu Musim Ketiga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah yang datang\Nharusnya guru bahasa Jepang?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, umm, gadis golden twintail di situ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama saya Inda Karane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Thank you, Ninja Karane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar Inda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}You tadi memotong pasti karena\NI am teacher bahasa Jepang
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi malah mirip teacher bahasa Inggris, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, karena baju Ibu seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terpaku pada penampilan luar\Nitu tidak baik, lho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa bilang teacher dari Amerika\Nonly mengajar bahasa Inggris?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa hukum mengatur teacher\Nharus selalu berpakaian rapi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini alasannya Japan people\Nvery-very kasihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia itu boleh hidup lebih bebas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am datang dari negara kebebasan, Amerika,\Nuntuk mengajari kalian kebebasan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengajar bahasa Jepang, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}School people di sini very-very\Nsuka membantah teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Freedom punyamu excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, bahasa Inggris Ibu\Nkenapa kacau begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am native bahasa Inggris,\Njadi Japan people tidak akan paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kira aku bodoh, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Su-Sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Japanese school boy, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boy dengan alis tebal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama saya Aijo Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aijo Boy, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepulang sekolah nanti\Nkelas tambahan dengan I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alismu mengganggu pelajaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudnya itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am tidak begitu paham bahasa Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal guru bahasa Jepang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang ke negaramu sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Anu, Bu Naddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di momen ini, perasaan tokoh utama serta\Nkenangan yang ditinggalkan sang Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan soal pertanyaannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa Ibu tidak terlalu dekat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masalahnya no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bermasalah atau tidak, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini jarak yang normal kalau di Amerika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi, ini di Jepang!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Aijo Boy tidak suka sepulang sekolah\Nada kelas berdua dengan I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya tidak suka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo Boy itu very-very cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bu Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, Japanese boy yang beringas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekadar hug itu sapaan di Amerika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo Boy ternyata seorang shy boy, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Naddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini juga bentuk sapaan di Amerika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, yang barusan bukan sapaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am sepertinya jatuh cinta ke Aijo Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham kamu mau bilang apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo Boy adalah seorang murid,\NI am seorang guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta yang not justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, tidak masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia itu harusnya hidup dengan bebas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta itu haruslah perfect freedom\Ndari heart sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Aijo Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berpacaranlah dengan I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Naddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu sebenarnya orang Jepang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu mahir bahasa Jepang untuk\Njadi guru dan mengajar di Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kukira Ibu orang yang begitu suka\Nbudaya Jepang dan giat mempelajarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, pola pikir Ibu begitu Amerika
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bahasa Inggrisnya juga aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, barusan itu membuatku yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan secara global, yang punya budaya\Nmemulai hubungan dengan menyatakan cinta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya Jepang dan beberapa negara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan orang Amerika sendiri\Ntidak melakukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru pertama kalinya jatuh cinta,\Nsampai lupa dengan sekitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, I am kelepasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setingnya seperti itu, kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Naddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama dan diri Ibu itu siapa sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, selesai sudah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di-Diriku putri sulung keluarga Yamato,\NYamato Nadeshiko, 24 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahasa Inggrisku sangat payah\Ndan tidak bisa jadi guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lahir dan dibesarkan di Jepang,\N100% produk Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang Jepang tulen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Naddy itu dari Nadeshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan dari Nadya, atau semacamnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa jadi guru di sekolah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am ingin jadi teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan modal nekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Imut sekali!\NKamu diterima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Hahari!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal bilang datang dari Amerika,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kemarin aku ke sana dan pulang\Nsetelah lima menit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendalami sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketahuan...\NSudah ketahuan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tidak bisa memainkan\Nkoto dengan benar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu putri sulung keluarga Yamato\Nyang terhormat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya malu jadi orang Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Renungkan kesalahanmu di gudang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, sulit bergerak dengan kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, aku juga tidak suka\Nmemainkan koto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tiap hari harus pakai kimono\Nyang tidak kusuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tiap hari aku harus\Nberlatih yang tidak kusuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena aku terlahir sebagai\Nputri sulung keluarga Yamato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena, aku orang Jepang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Barang-barang jatuh karena pintunya\Ndibanting sekeras itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku selalu disuruh menutup pelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wow, Superman!\NDia sangat kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak ini menonton TV\Nsambil makan piza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memeluk popcorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia minum Cola 2 liter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata orang-orang itu boleh sebebas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pakai sepatu di dalam rumah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan rambutmu?!\NJuga pakaianmu itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu aib bagi keluarga Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aib untuk orang Jepang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menginjakkan kakimu\Ndi rumah ini lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fakyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang Jepang tapi rambutnya diwarnai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juga berpenampilan begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin mau menjadikan\Norang sememalukan ini sebagai pacar...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada juga\Nyang tidak ingin Ibu ceritakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma, kalau setelah ini kita pacaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi ingin lebih tahu soal Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kamu mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan orang Jepang yang pura-pura\Njadi orang Amerika sepertiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apanya yang malu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu berusaha jadi diri yang diinginkan
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta menunjukkannya tanpa ditutup-tutupi\Nitu kurasa sangat luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, berpacaranlah denganku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dik Aijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo, aku juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya tidak begitu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Naddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aijo Boy...\N- Dik Aijo itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- I am...\N- Bagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Captain...\N- Orang yang paling hebat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- America...\N- Seperti negara yang bebas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aijo Boy, I am Captain America!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oleh karena itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kalian menerima\NBu Naddy sebagai pacar baruku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ternyata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumpulan orang yang begitu freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta yang freedom sesuai keinginan sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang yang seperti buku cinta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pujian apa pun akan membuatmu senang, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kalian kumpulan yang freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sayang sekali kalian semua\Npakai seragam school yang sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti I am yang menunjukkan cinta\Nke Amerika dengan seluruh badan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tunjukkan penampilan kalian\Nyang lebih bebas lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, kayaknya seru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kupesankan semua pakaian\Nyang kalian mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka kemudian memikirkan\N"penampilan bebas" yang diinginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kugambar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu selalu saja tangkas dalam segala hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlihatkan pada I am,\Nwujud kebebasan Eiai Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gambar tangan tidak hanya\Ngaris lurus saja, lho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu maunya gimana, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kaku maksimal dan no freedom sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memang benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya giliran saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}You semua bagaimana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka semua bilang suka\Ndengan penampilanku sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seragam pelayan yang saya terima\Ndari Nyonya Hahari ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju yang menutupi diriku\Nsebanyak mungkin ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak bisa disebut bebas!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat heart kalian jadi lebih freedom lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan ke atasan juga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski atasan, harus tetap freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betapa tegasnya ke orang lain\Ndan diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, pokoknya aku tidak boleh menyerah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kugambar dengan segenap jiwa raga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tegas banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Come on, yang serius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Happy birthday, hasrat terpendam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hasrat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}No defense!\NGo serang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bebas itu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak paham!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kacamatamu jatuh, Kak!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dianya sendiri begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dikira dia ini siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada pacar baru, rasanya malah seperti\Nada guru baru yang bergabung.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju pesanan kalian
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah datang, lho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini besoknya banget, lho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu, tahu? Kekuatan uang itu\Nbisa mewujudkan hal semustahil apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pasang muka saat Ibunda\Nmasih jadi antagonis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang itu saat dia masih waras.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar Mama yang melepas bajumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Ibunda malah kemari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurumi itu di sana, lho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dioper ke aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meme, tetekmu gede sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?! Ja-Jangan dilihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meme malah kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini wujud kebebasan kalian semua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu cepat, belum dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanganku tidak sampai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bajumu itu gimana, sih?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan rendah hati\Nizinkan saya yang pertama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karakter anjing Sanrio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Imut sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Detak jantungku bisa berhenti...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aduh, itu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya fitur ekor yang bergerak\Nmengikuti perasaan hati!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau membunuhku, ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini wujud kebebasan Kak Mei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa sekali, ya, Bu Naddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini masih belum bisa disebut bebas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Aku giliran kedua."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan putri di dunia nyata?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan putri memang nyata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.40,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi ini perasaan ingin\Nmengajaknya jalan-jalan di Disneyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma ibu bawa anaknya jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya giliran saya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seragam bocil adik polwan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku rela ditangkap kalau\Npolisinya seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Semoga kalimat itu bukanlah\Nprediksi di masa depan."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Peri Makaron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, Dik Kurumi ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata aslinya pengin tampil imut begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemarin pagi aku lihat setrika teflon,\Njadinya pengin makan makaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untung bukan pengin makan setrikanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku minta dibuatkan\Npakai makaron betulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata sekadar nafsu makan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, mari kita lanjutkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang giliranku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihatlah aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kau ini bos terakhir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanlah aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelacur!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantik dan berfungsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baju renang balap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini yang dari seri Bintang Raksasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengambang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Malah direndam formalin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cairan yang tidak terlalu bahaya\Nuntuk tubuh manusia buatanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bukan sepenuhnya aman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paling kencing jadi sedikit kuning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya vitamin B?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya giliranku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malah jadi Kak Mimimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Betapa cantiknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin bisa tampil percaya diri\Ntanpa merasa malu seperti Kak Mimimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu dilanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Mimimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu ingin jadi seperti diriku\Nyang cantiknya luar biasa, kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Mimimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, bukankah dirimu juga cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu rahasia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Su-Sudah kubilang, aku tidak cantik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kabur lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Berikutnya aku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang Pria Karet itu lagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin jadi laki-laki kuat demi\Nmelindungi keluarga yang kucintai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski nyawaku taruhannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Cenut!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kenapa bukan kostum\Nsetelah jeda dua tahun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, soalnya aku masih belum bisa pakai Haki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, dia pikir kelak bisa pakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya Rentaro suatu saat bakal bisa pakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikutnya giliranmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.46,0:17:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukannya apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma tidak enak badan, mau ke UKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Memangnya aku kamu...!\N- Jangan manja minta durasi buat dirimu sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gaya feminin yang lembut dan menggemaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waduh, Karane ini imut banget, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik!\NJangan lihat ke sini!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karane cewek paling imut\Ndan lembut di dunia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang berisik, pergi sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, pukulannya juga terasa lembut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Saking kuatnya, sampai bikin\Nindra rasa sakit mati."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Hahari, selanjutnya dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah melihat betapa\Nimutnya kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, rasanya aku tidak usah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan apa yang putrimu lakukan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak kelas Hahari!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kalau aku bebas jadi apa saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kupikir pasti menyenangkan kalau bisa\Njadi anak SMA lagi bersama kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ta-Tapi, rasanya memang memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bilang apa Anda ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda sangat imut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih cocok banget jadi anak SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya dibanding dirimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Hahari yang sekarang\Nmemang anak SMA seperti kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Hahari, cocok sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunda...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari lubuk hatinya, Hakari berpikir\Nkalau itu jelas-jelas "tempat begituan".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, sadar akan situasi sekitar,\Ndia pun ikut berbaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya sudah selesai\Nmenunjukkan penampilannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana menurut Bu Naddy?\NPenampilan bebas kami ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paling tidak harusnya ada satu\Nyang memenuhi standar kebebasan Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mengenali kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah berbeda dari saat\Nmenyembunyikan diri dengan seragam school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}You semua sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan lagi kumpulan freedom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, Freedom Avengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am susah payah menahan tangis\Ndan melihat dengan muka datar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang setegas itu akhirnya\Nmenghargai kerja keras kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelatih Naddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh sebuah fight yang hebat\Ndari kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilan yang very freedom luar biasa!\NI am thank you very much ke kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kami juga berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Berkat Anda, kami bisa tampil seperti ini."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya seperti Kontes Masquerade Kincan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Bu Naddy tidak setegas itu ke kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak akan sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ingin berpenampilan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bebas mengikuti perasaanku sendiri\Nternyata sesusah ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku saja tidak sadar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau selama ini aku menahan\Nperasaanku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua rasanya sudah cukup bebas, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya juga berterima kasih\Npada Anda, Nona Naddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian memang people dengan beautiful heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am ingin menunjukkan ini ke kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SIM lama yang I am miliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yamato Nadeshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu orang Jepang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:21:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini harusnya rahasia Bu Naddy\Nyang tidak ingin diungkap ke siapa pun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.20,0:21:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian semua telah menunjukkan\Nkebebasan yang sungguh luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}And bagi I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}inilah bukti ingin menjadi\Nanggota family kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pelatih Naddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I am teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Pakaian polisi itu,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"sangat cocok denganmu."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Shizuka juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu mau?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.58,0:21:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mama boleh ikut memakanmu tidak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua untuk Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan gunakan diriku untuk latihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya beban lepas dari my shoulder\Ndan I am jadi lebih freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini, I am dalam horror\Ntidak ingin mengungkapkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Secret kalau I am Japan people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka day ini coming juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semua karena Rentaro Boy\Nmenebak rahasia I am
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mengatakan kalau ini\Nbukan hal yang memalukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kok...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rentaro Boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu Naddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takdir yang dipisahkan oleh hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wow!
